.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-7::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, may, september, june, april
5 different pets are kept: rabbit, goldfish, horse, cat, ferret
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
3. the person who's birthday is in may is in the middle##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
8. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
9. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| Birthday   | april       | september   | may    | june    | march |
| Pet        | horse | rabbit | goldfish | ferret | cat     |

