.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-8::.
5 different games are played: go, snooker, mah-jongg, whist, canasta
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: reggae, r&b, techno, blues, d&b
1. the fan of techno is the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing go is on the left of the fan of blues##1
3. the person playing whist is in an even position##4
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of reggae is between the fan of blues and the fan of d&b##2
6. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
7. the fan of techno is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4    |    5    |
| Game      | mah-jongg  | go       | snooker      | whist  | canasta   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | reggae | blues | r&b | techno |

