.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-9::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: drawing, card-games, woodworking, puzzles, singing
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: rose, sunflower, lily, amaryllis, tulip
1. the person who growsrose is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who growsrose##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
7. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
8. the person who growssunflower is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby   | singing | card-games | woodworking     | drawing | puzzles |
| Flower           | sunflower | rose     | lily | tulip    | amaryllis      |

