.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-11::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: indie, country, punk, techno, soul
The people have 5 different hobbies: woodworking, collecting, video-games, skydiving, sudoku
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
3. the fan of indie is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the fan of punk##1
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
7. the fan of country is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |     4      |   5    |
| Music-Genre    | country    | soul  | indie      | techno     | punk |
| Hobby   | woodworking | collecting | skydiving | video-games | sudoku |

