.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-12::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: horror, scientific, animation, action, mystery
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, november, december, september, june
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is the person watching horror movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is in the middle##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person watching scientific movies##2
7. the person who's birthday is in november is in an odd position##4
8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |   3   |     4     |     5      |
| Movie-Genre        | action | mystery | horror  | animation | scientific     |
| Birthday   | november  | december     | june | january      | september |

