.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-13::.
House: futuristic, colonial, farmhouse, victorian, tower
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, soccer, volleyball, tennis
1. the victorian house is in an even position##4
2. the tower house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1
4. the victorian house is on the right of the colonial house##1
5. the farmhouse house is in an even position##4
6. the colonial house is between the person who's sport is climbing and the farmhouse house##2
7. the tower house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5     |
| House      | tower       | farmhouse | colonial | victorian   | futuristic   |
| Sport   | volleyball | sailing | tennis  | climbing | soccer |

