.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-14::.
House: art-deco, gothic-revival, cape-cod, colonial, ranch-style
There are 5 different favourite colors: grey, lavender, azure, red, coral
1. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes red##1
2. the art-deco house is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
4. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
5. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4
6. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
7. the person who likes red is between the person who likes lavender and the gothic-revival house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5      |
| House    | ranch-style   | colonial  | gothic-revival     | art-deco | cape-cod |
| Color   | grey | azure | coral | red | lavender      |

