.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-15::.
5 different pets are kept: bird, dog, hamster, hedgehog, rat
City: venice, boston, rome, berlin, new-york
1. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
2. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
3. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
4. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
5. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
6. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
7. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4
8. the person traveling to berlin is in the middle##1
9. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3       |    4     |    5    |
| Pet   | dog  | hamster    | hedgehog | bird   | rat |
| City   | new-york | boston | berlin    | venice | rome |

