.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-16::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, volleyball, weightlifting, climbing, rowing
The people have 5 different hobbies: writing, gardening, rock-climbing, woodworking, baking
1. the person who's sport is climbing is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |    3     |    4     |   5    |
| Sport           | baseball | rowing | weightlifting | climbing | volleyball   |
| Hobby   | gardening       | rock-climbing            | writing    | woodworking     | baking |

