.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-17::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, november, may, february, august
The people have 5 different hobbies: camping, video-games, card-games, magic-tricks, woodworking
1. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's hobby is camping##2
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |    3     |    4    |   5   |
| Birthday   | june | february | may     | august     | november |
| Hobby     | magic-tricks   | video-games   | camping | card-games | woodworking  |

