.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-18::.
House: gothic-revival, wooden, futuristic, cape-cod, townhouse
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: salsa, electronic, folk, soul, trance
1. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
2. the fan of electronic is in an even position##4
3. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of soul##1
4. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
5. the wooden house is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
6. the fan of trance is on the far left or far right##3
7. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
8. the townhouse house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
9. the futuristic house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |   4    |     5      |
| House   | gothic-revival | wooden | townhouse     | futuristic | cape-cod |
| Music-Genre     | soul       | electronic   | folk | salsa   | trance        |

