.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-19::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, scooter, trike, boat, van
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, aristoff, alhambra, baccarat, chaman
1. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
2. the alhambra-smoker is the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
5. the person driving the van is between the person driving the bus and the chaman-smoker##2
6. the aristoff-smoker is between the person driving the boat and the chaman-smoker##2
7. the baccarat-smoker is in an odd position##4
8. the chaman-smoker is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Transport         | boat | trike | scooter | van | bus     |
| Cigar   | baccarat    | aristoff   | chaman       | alhambra | vegafina |

