1. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the person who growslily is between the person who growsazalea and the person who growstulip##2
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is in the middle##1
6. the person who growsazalea is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
7. the person who's sport is baseball is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Sport   | weightlifting | cycling      | soccer | snowboarding     | baseball      |
| Flower     | azalea | lily | tulip | amaryllis | begonia |

 